# Flutter OCR Scanner Assignment

A Flutter OCR-based application that scans and extracts structured data from:

* Credit / Debit Cards
* Bank Passbooks

## Features

* Card Scanner
* Passbook Scanner
* OCR Text Extraction
* Card Validation using Luhn Algorithm
* Manual Parsing Logic
* Camera & Gallery Support
* GetX State Management
* Modern UI Design

## Tech Stack

* Flutter
* GetX
* Google ML Kit OCR
* Image Picker

## Run Project

```bash
flutter pub get
flutter run
```

## Build APK

```bash
flutter build apk --release
```

